body:
@F3PiX that's okay, I understand :)
so, it only took one more change for it to work properly (with your restoring the change, the menu was stuck collapsed in responsive view): the `collapse` class needed to be moved outside of the unordered list into its own div. I've also added `role="navigation"` to improve accessibility. 
This should now work properly as intended, and I think we can merge the PR. Great work Maud!! :tada:
